4244&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1544244%26target%3D2&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=204745d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1544244%26target%3D2&h=cc7bc6b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1544244&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 南韓獨立檢察組要求進入青瓦台總統府進行搜查取證及對朴槿惠進行問話，但相關官員以「青瓦台是涉及軍事和工作機密的重要場所」為由禁止檢察組人員入內。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00014/1486146128759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00014%2F1486146128759&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5ee44d8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00014%2F1486146128759&h=30fec770\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00014/1486146128759</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170204/00180_023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170204%2F00180_023.html&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=756535a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170204/00180_023.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1544241&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1544241%26target%3D2&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9aed724b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1544241%26target%3D2&h=d15475a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1544241&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 瓦努阿圖北部托爾巴省（Torba）實施禁止進口外國食品的計劃，首階段當地旅店將停止向客人提供外國進口食物，只提供當地種植有機農產品，而未來兩年將透過立法全面禁止進口外國食物。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00014/1486146131161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00014%2F1486146131161&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=96a58fce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00014%2F1486146131161&h=3d81331f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00014/1486146131161</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊集中帖<br />\n(想了解呢個post既來歷,檢索返以往既每日用2分鐘睇新聞,可以入去呢條link):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/57314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/57314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日新聞<br />\n(想追返尋日既post就入去):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/105442/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/105442/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Facebook Page<br />\n(如果想係facebook睇既歡迎like下,每日朝早8點/9點/10點會分批post每日新聞,方便大家係facebook都睇到):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkintelligentsiaplatform/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkintelligentsiaplatform%2F&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKqW